other objects.description: Large reels most likely containing cable or similar material, and smaller objects scattered on the side of the road, positioned within an industrial or construction setting.
other objects.explanation: These objects are in the periphery of the roadway and do not pose a direct obstacle to the ego car's path, but they indicate a possible industrial area or construction zone where additional hazards or unexpected road conditions may occur.

suggestions: Proceed with caution due to the industrial setting. Be vigilant for any unscheduled movements from adjacent lots, heavy machinery, or workers that may affect road safety. Maintain a safe speed and be ready to adjust the driving path in case of any obstacles or vehicles entering the roadway.
